---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Website Speed Optimization - Make Your Astro Site Lightning Fast"
  description="Expert website speed optimization services. Turn your slow site into a performance powerhouse with Core Web Vitals optimization and technical improvements."
  keywords="website speed optimization, Core Web Vitals, performance optimization, page speed improvement, site speed audit">
  
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Turn Your Site Into a <em>Speed Demon</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Already have an Astro site but it's not performing? We'll optimize every millisecond to ensure your site 
          loads instantly and converts like crazy.
        </p>
        <div class="speed-stats">
          <div class="before-after">
            <div class="stat-column">
              <h3>Typical Before</h3>
              <div class="stat-bad">3.2s load time</div>
              <div class="stat-bad">67 PageSpeed</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">‚Üí</div>
            <div class="stat-column">
              <h3>After Optimization</h3>
              <div class="stat-good">0.8s load time</div>
              <div class="stat-good">98 PageSpeed</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Optimize My Site</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="speed-problems">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Speed Killers We Fix</h2>
      <div class="problems-grid">
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">üêå</div>
          <h3>Unoptimized Images</h3>
          <p>Massive image files killing load times. We'll compress and convert to modern formats without quality loss.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">üì¶</div>
          <h3>Bloated JavaScript</h3>
          <p>Unnecessary code and unused libraries slowing everything down. We'll trim the fat and optimize what remains.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">üîÑ</div>
          <h3>Render-Blocking Resources</h3>
          <p>CSS and JavaScript blocking the critical rendering path. We'll optimize loading order for instant rendering.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">üì±</div>
          <h3>Poor Mobile Performance</h3>
          <p>Desktop might be fast, but mobile users are suffering. We'll ensure blazing speed on all devices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">üîó</div>
          <h3>Third-Party Scripts</h3>
          <p>Analytics, chat widgets, and other external scripts dragging you down. We'll optimize their loading impact.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">‚ö°</div>
          <h3>Suboptimal Hosting</h3>
          <p>Great code on slow servers equals disappointing results. We'll recommend and configure optimal hosting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="optimization-process">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Speed Optimization Process</h2>
      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Performance Audit</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive analysis using Lighthouse, WebPageTest, and Core Web Vitals tools to identify bottlenecks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Image Optimization</h3>
            <p>Convert to WebP/AVIF, implement responsive images, and add lazy loading for optimal visual performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Code Optimization</h3>
            <p>Minify CSS/JS, remove unused code, implement critical CSS inlining, and optimize bundle sizes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-marker">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Caching & Delivery</h3>
            <p>Configure optimal caching strategies, CDN setup, and edge delivery for global performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="core-web-vitals">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Core Web Vitals Mastery</h2>
      <div class="vitals-grid">
        <div class="vital-card">
          <div class="vital-icon">üöÄ</div>
          <h3>Largest Contentful Paint (LCP)</h3>
          <p>We'll get your main content loading in under 1.2 seconds through image optimization, critical resource prioritization, and server response optimization.</p>
          <div class="target">Target: &lt; 1.2s</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vital-card">
          <div class="vital-icon">‚ö°</div>
          <h3>First Input Delay (FID)</h3>
          <p>Optimize JavaScript execution and main thread work to ensure your site responds to user interactions in under 50ms.</p>
          <div class="target">Target: &lt; 50ms</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vital-card">
          <div class="vital-icon">üìê</div>
          <h3>Cumulative Layout Shift (CLS)</h3>
          <p>Eliminate layout shifts by properly sizing images, reserving space for ads, and optimizing font loading strategies.</p>
          <div class="target">Target: &lt; 0.05</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="optimization-features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What Gets Optimized</h2>
      <div class="features-checklist">
        <div class="feature-section">
          <h3>üñºÔ∏è Image Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>WebP and AVIF conversion</li>
            <li>Responsive image implementation</li>
            <li>Lazy loading configuration</li>
            <li>Image compression without quality loss</li>
            <li>Modern format delivery</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-section">
          <h3>‚öôÔ∏è Code Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>CSS and JavaScript minification</li>
            <li>Dead code elimination</li>
            <li>Critical CSS inlining</li>
            <li>Bundle size optimization</li>
            <li>Tree shaking implementation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-section">
          <h3>üåê Delivery Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>CDN configuration and setup</li>
            <li>Browser caching optimization</li>
            <li>Gzip/Brotli compression</li>
            <li>Resource hint implementation</li>
            <li>HTTP/2 optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-section">
          <h3>üì± Mobile Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Touch target sizing</li>
            <li>Mobile-specific optimizations</li>
            <li>Viewport configuration</li>
            <li>Mobile Core Web Vitals</li>
            <li>Progressive loading strategies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="results-guarantee">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guarantee-content">
        <h2>Performance Guarantee</h2>
        <p>We guarantee your site will achieve:</p>
        <div class="guarantee-metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-number">90+</span>
            <span class="metric-label">PageSpeed Score</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-number">&lt;1.5s</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Load Time</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-number">100%</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Core Web Vitals Pass</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="guarantee-text">If we don't hit these targets, we'll keep optimizing until we do‚Äîat no extra cost.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Stop Losing Customers to Slow Load Times</h2>
      <p>Every second of delay costs you conversions. Let's make your site blazing fast.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Speed Up My Site</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.service-hero {
  padding: calc(80px + var(--space-16)) 0 var(--space-16);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
}

.before-after {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  align-items: center;
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}

.stat-bad {
  background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: var(--space-2);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  margin: var(--space-2) 0;
}

.stat-good {
  background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: var(--space-2);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  margin: var(--space-2) 0;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.speed-problems {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.problems-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.problem-item {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  text-align: center;
  border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
}

.problem-icon {
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.optimization-process {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
}

.process-timeline {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--space-8);
}

.timeline-step {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.step-marker {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.core-web-vitals {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.vitals-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.vital-card {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  text-align: center;
}

.vital-icon {
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.target {
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-top: var(--space-4);
  display: inline-block;
}

.optimization-features {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
}

.features-checklist {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.feature-section {
  background: var(--color-white);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
}

.results-guarantee {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1) 0%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1) 100%);
  text-align: center;
}

.guarantee-content {
  background: var(--color-white);
  padding: var(--space-8);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.guarantee-metrics {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}

.metric {
  text-align: center;
}

.metric-number {
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #f59e0b;
}


.cta-section {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: #1a1a2e;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .before-after {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .timeline-step {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
  }
}
</style>